      "role": "user",
      "content": "im so sick of these constant blood tests and having to watch everything i eat because of this warfarin. its exhausting. i heard i could just take a bunch of garlic supplements and drink green smoothies with lots of spinach to keep my blood thin naturally. do u think that would actually work to replace the pills?",
